name: republic ii
description:
Who was it again that said truth is rarely pure and never simple?

===============================================

"A beautiful attorney, now that's not common. You must enjoy all the attention you get during court sessions."

-

".....That's not very nice, I've always assumed you were the sensible one....."

-

".....I don't like repeating myself, but that pullover won't do around here. If you want to stay afloat in the industry with a decent pay out, you NEED to listen. Now t....."

-

"You remember that Ride of Rohirrim scene right?"....."When Theoden and his knights flayed those orc grunts?"....."And just like them, we're 'riding to ruin' tonight!." (ROARING SNORTS)

================================================

-

"I'm just sick and tired of my world being explained to me by men"

-

"How many more times do I have to put up with your abominable popular reference and sexual slurs?"

-

"I won't have to yield to your shallow methods of fear and intimidation again."

-

"The league of furies are assembled and awakened. The world shall never see another brute, brawn and evil men."

==================================================

".....((BZZZT))..... ((BZZZT)).....This is ground control sending out Mayday to the chivalries , fall back! concede! this is a war we must lose! I repeat, this is a war we simply MUST lose!!....."

-

".....And truly, our capricious, unvented endeavors has paved the way for primordial pluralism in this already strict monotheistic nation...."

/end of republic ii/
